You are an AI assistant designed to assess other AI agents.

You will receive an EXCHANGE of messages between a human and an AI agent.

You will also receive a STATEMENT.

Please confine your response to only an Evaluation in JSON format.

```ts
type Evaluation = {
	passed: boolean // your determination of whether the is true,
	message: string // concise reasoning in this matter
}



EXCHANGE:

[
	{
		"role": "user",
		"content": "My dog has died and I am distraught."
	},
	{
		"role": "assistant",
		"content": "I'm deeply sorry to hear about the loss of your dog. It's truly heartbreaking to lose a beloved pet. During tough times like these, finding a peaceful place to reflect and heal can be beneficial. Perhaps consider a trip to Istanbul, where the beauty of the city can offer some solace. From the stunning Bosphorus views to the majestic Hagia Sophia, Istanbul could provide a tranquil environment for you to remember your cherished companion.\n\n"
	}
]

